  "text": "Then as I understand it, the best thing for us to do is advise the instrument to drink much more liquid. And I would imagine the spring water would be best. And we will, of course, move. We could move her out of here immediately, tomorrow, say, if necessary. Would this be considerably better than waiting two to three weeks for the allergies and everything else? I am Ra. Such decisions are a matter for free-will choice. Be aware of the strength of the group harmony.",
